{"tid":569869,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【車內燒炭】失蹤兩天沙田「尋回」　LEGO達人七人車內燒炭亡","createTime":"2018-02-23T06:08:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-23T07:05:37.000Z","uid":10958,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"640b068ef10109c590e978cc5cb8aa85a5dfb3bc","tid":569869,"uid":10958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:08:16.000Z","msg":"<strong>【車內燒炭】失蹤兩天沙田「尋回」　LEGO達人七人車內燒炭亡</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/162083/thumbnail/779c3aa835c4931c8ad6afb0ec491f0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F162083%2Fthumbnail%2F779c3aa835c4931c8ad6afb0ec491f0b.jpg&h=134d8248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日中午12時許，警方接報指，沙田安明街港鐵石門站對開，一輛掛着「P牌」的七人車內有一名男子陷入昏迷。警員及救護員隨即趕往現場，但打開車門發現男子已經死亡，車內有燒炭痕迹，懷疑他自殺。警員其後留守現場調查男子尋死原因及聯絡其家人了解詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1227456/xlarge/c4a088f0cbeffd9f4f045106d343af46.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1227456%2Fxlarge%2Fc4a088f0cbeffd9f4f045106d343af46.jpg&h=d7588356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">劉以良生前曾以LEGO砌出珍寶海鮮坊。（香港樂高迷用戶組 fb圖片）</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劉以良為LEGO迷，他曾接受傳媒訪問表示，自己砌LEGO已有數十年經驗。他小時候已渴望砌LEGO，但因家庭經濟關係未能買到，後來有親戚送了數盒LEGO給他，從此就沉醉在LEGO世界，砌完又拆，拆完又砌。 長大後他買了一間屋，作他的LEGO天地，亦與朋友共同租用迷你倉放LEGO。 他曾參加過一個砌出香港特色景點的LEGO創作比賽，當時他以珍寶海鮮舫參賽，花了兩個多星期完成，共使用了5000多塊積木， 而這個珍寶海鮮舫亦成為當年的入圍作品。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1226402/xlarge/2310ec1b073bf95f40adc4f436ab1999.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1226402%2Fxlarge%2F2310ec1b073bf95f40adc4f436ab1999.jpg&h=fd9b9a9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">七人車停泊在港鐵石門站對開路面。 （賴俊傑攝）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/162083/-%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%A7%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD-%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A9%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0-%E5%B0%8B%E5%9B%9E-LEGO%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%A7%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD%E4%BA%A1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2F162083%2F-%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2592%25E7%2582%25AD-%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E5%2585%25A9%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E6%25B2%2599%25E7%2594%25B0-%25E5%25B0%258B%25E5%259B%259E-LEGO%25E9%2581%2594%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%2583%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25BB%258A%25E5%2585%25A7%25E7%2587%2592%25E7%2582%25AD%25E4%25BA%25A1&d=czLhboHiFNV%2BMEKCeGGQ0%2BargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=b15fe5f9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/162083/-%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%A7%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD-%E5%A4%B1%E8%B9%A4%E5%85%A9%E5%A4%A9%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0-%E5%B0%8B%E5%9B%9E-LEGO%E9%81%94%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%83%E4%BA%BA%E8%BB%8A%E5%85%A7%E7%87%92%E7%82%AD%E4%BA%A1</a>"},{"pid":"06ee934665e280b0f1caae8fb515a84d6baca56b","tid":569869,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:09:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c445d6796ff69140ad04514129dbeab171edb994","tid":569869,"uid":26156,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:11:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae7dfb5223ddbe53cf8ed14086ba7853693b5483","tid":569869,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:12:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b3ae51488c745b3200eb38de65aebae4942c674","tid":569869,"uid":88029,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-23T06:16:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"39e462fbb9fefd83de69c117afc756779858e828","tid":569869,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6b3ae51488c745b3200eb38de65aebae4942c674","tid":56986